<!DOCTYPE html>
<title>CSS Test: Test declaring a variable whose value is "unset" where there is no variable to inherit from.</title>
<link rel="author" title="Cameron McCormack" href="mailto:cam@mcc.id.au">
<link rel="help" href="http://www.w3.org/TR/css-variables--2975/#defining-variables">
<p><p><p>This text must be green.</p></p></p>
<style>
p {
  color: red;
}
p {
  color: orange;
  --a: unset;
  color: var(--a,green);
}
</style>
